*Udati* se za nju bila je najbolja odluka koju je mogao da donese (Marrying her was the best decision he could make).

Imao je sreće da je uspeo da *udati* devojku o koju je oduvek maštao (He was lucky to be able to marry the girl he had always dreamed of).

Mnogo godina je trebalo da se *udaju* (It took many years for them to get married).

Nije bilo lako da *udatim* sina kada se približila njegova večita mladost (It wasn't easy to marry off my son as he approached his eternal youth).

Njeni roditelji su se borili da je što pre *udate* (Her parents fought to marry her off as soon as possible).